results.title: Live Laugh Love Wall Art Sticker,  Inspirational Quote, Modern  Room Decor, Removable Vinyl Decal
results.description:
Live Laugh Love wall art sticker are a simple and creative way to transform your room and give some personality to any blank wall. Vinyl graphics instantly add colour and make an interesting focal point. When the time comes to remove wall art, just gently peel off all parts of the sticker and you are done. Wall will remain just like it was if it is done properly. 

DECAL COMES AS A LAYERED PIECE
Top layer (clear application tape).
Middle layer (actual vinyl sticker).
Backing layer (glossy wax paper the wall sticker lays on). 

APPLICATION INSTRUCTION 
Care needs to be taken when fitting wall sticker, as it is NOT A REUSABLE item. 
Take your time for the best results.
1. Clean up the surface and ensure it's dry. Allow at least 2 weeks after wall painting.
2. Unroll decal sheet and lay it flat on a hard surface, press and firmly drag over the entire graphic with the plastic card to adhere the vinyl sticker to the clear application tape.
3. Peel away from backing paper. Vinyl sticker should remain on clear application tape.
4. Place decal on surface carefully. Use a plastic card to smooth the graphic onto surface. 
5. Remove the application tape by slowly peeling it off starting from the corner.
6. Use a soft cloth to press the entire sticker into surface. 
WE ARE NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR ANY ERRORS MADE DURING THE APPLICATION

PRODUCT DESCRIPTION 
Premium quality matte vinyl. Decals are good for both: outdoor and indoor applications and will last from 3 to 7 years. No clear background, just graphic. Vinyl sticker is removable but NOT reusable. Product can be applied on: paint, plastic, glass, vinyl, car, fiberglass, wood (painted) and any other smooth, slightly textured surface. 

SIZE, COLOUR & FINISH
Wall decals are matt. 
Available in various sizes and colours.
Please check drop down menu for all options. 
(Images displayed are for reference only do not reflect the exact size. Colors may appear different on your monitor depending on your settings).

WHAT YOU GET WITH THIS LISTING
One wall decal in preferred size & colour, test sticker and instruction.

SHIPPING
UK 2-5 days, Europe 5-14 days, USA and Rest of World 5-14 days 

CUSTOM ORDERS & WHOLESALE

There’s not a whole lot we can do when the tracking info shows it as being delivered. Please check with everyone in your household as someone else might have brought it in. Sometimes we have heard of a package going to a neighbor mistakenly or being left at a different/side door. In our experience, usually the package is located.
Most orders are shipped via UPS Mail Innovations or UPS Surepost, and final delivery is by the USPS so we also suggest having the customer contact their local post office and many times they can get in touch with the actual person who delivered it and see if they recall where they left it. It’s best to do that soon after it’s marked as delivered.
💕 NO TRACKING OR NO MOVEMENT
If a package does not show any movement and has passed the allotted time for delivery we will send a new package at our cost to the customer.  We may ask you to check to very the address or supply us with a new shipping address.
SIZING EXCHANGE
We don't offer exchanges or refunds in those situations.
💕 PRODUCT ISSUE
If it is an issue on our end where we sent out the wrong product, wrong size, bad graphic just send us a picture of what you have  received for quality control purposes and we can offer a refund or replacement once the issue is deemed our fault.
US customers have up to 30 days after the shipped date and international customers have up to 60 days after the shipped date.
What we need to make a replacement order:
1.	Please provide the name and email.
2.	Please provide the order number.
3.	Please provide picture of wrong/ damaged item And Shipping Label.
Once we receive this we will print a replacement product and send it right out!
